			"**Scheduler matters for tests** — The second argument is a `SchedulerLike`. In production code you omit it (defaults to `asyncScheduler`). In Vitest/TestScheduler marble tests you must pass the `TestScheduler`'s virtual time scheduler, otherwise your tests run against real wall-clock time and will be flaky.",
