		"related": "| Operator | Key difference | Choose when |\n|----------|---------------|-------------|\n| `defer` + `finalize` | More ergonomic setup/teardown | You don't need a typed resource object |\n| `new Observable(subscriber => { ... return teardown })` | Full manual control | You need custom subscription logic beyond what `using` offers |\n| `fromEvent` | Specialised DOM-event listener | Just attaching a listener, no custom resource |\n| `shareReplay` | Shares one subscription | You want the resource and source shared |\n\n---",
